you were trying to send
Jack Harmon to his maker.

18:43.718 --> 18:44.980
Remember?

18:45.086 --> 18:46.610
Wait a second,
that was you?

18:48.156 --> 18:50.590
You know, l don't know
how to tell you this, but...

18:50.691 --> 18:51.783
you're dead.

18:51.859 --> 18:54.919
How do you think l got to be
the Clean Racing Fairy?

18:57.365 --> 18:59.856
