his best race car...

21:05.359 --> 21:07.623
he's gonna break
more than that.

21:07.695 --> 21:09.595
What are you
talking about?

21:10.164 --> 21:11.256
B.A.?

21:18.105 --> 21:19.766
l told you
you didn't wanna
do this, sucker.

21:24.245 --> 21:26.179
