28:48.188 --> 28:49.177
That's right.

28:49.456 --> 28:53.051
lt was his idea
to equalize the air-fuel
distribution, too.

28:53.127 --> 28:55.595
To Jack Harmon,
the old drunk, right?

28:55.663 --> 28:58.131
The old man,
he needs some love
and attention...

28:58.198 --> 29:00.257
