lt's time we had it out.

29:17.184 --> 29:19.880
lt's time you heard
how sick and tired
l am of your drinking...

29:19.953 --> 29:21.545
and your excuses
for everything.

29:21.622 --> 29:23.180
And you know what else,
Uncle John?

29:23.257 --> 29:24.884
He's always
badmouthing you.

29:24.958 --> 29:27.051
And he showed me
these newspaper clippings
to prove it.

29:27.127 --> 29:29.322
Well, l don't care
how many times
you tell me, Dad...

29:29.396 --> 29:31.864
l know he didn't commit
those crimes in the army.

29:31.965 --> 29:35.025
l know he's innocent.
And l know he's my friend!

29:38.138 --> 29:40.834
Well, you did it.
Congratulations.

29:41.575 --> 29:44.442
