You got even.

29:53.587 --> 29:55.885
Guess l'll go
relieve Murdock.

29:55.956 --> 29:57.617
Yeah, thanks, B.A.

29:59.093 --> 30:00.856
Feel like taking
a swing at me, Kid?

30:00.928 --> 30:02.395
No. Of course not.

30:02.463 --> 30:04.590
Then you shouldn't be
swinging at your father,
