didn't you, Kid?

30:12.573 --> 30:13.733
Yeah, you know l did.

30:14.007 --> 30:16.567
So did l. A long time ago.

30:16.643 --> 30:18.577
Your father and l,
both did.
What?

30:18.645 --> 30:20.545
Yeah. When we were
about your age...

30:21.381 --> 30:23.212
we both went after
the same girl.

30:23.550 --> 30:26.713
Your mother. She was
the most beautiful thing
you ever saw.

30:27.221 --> 30:29.348
And we were both
crazy about her.

30:29.790 --> 30:32.759
We both proposed,
and she had to choose
between us.

30:32.826 --> 30:33.918
No way.

30:33.994 --> 30:37.088
l don't believe she had
the chance to choose you
and she picks him.

30:37.164 --> 30:38.825
[laughing]
Oh, yes.

30:39.666 --> 30:43.466
She chose your father
for all the things he was
and l wasn't.

30:44.338 --> 30:45.828
Family-oriented...

30:45.906 --> 30:50.070
secure in his job,
and always there for her.

30:50.611 --> 30:54.411
And when she died, that's
when he started to drink.

30:54.882 --> 30:58.841
Now, maybe you and l could
help him find his way back.

30:59.887 --> 31:01.184
l don't know.

31:02.823 --> 31:04.120
