32:07.054 --> 32:08.817
Come on, Giancarlo.

32:09.056 --> 32:11.047
[gasping]
Easy does it.

32:15.596 --> 32:17.621
[in ltalian accent]
How are you today?

32:21.702 --> 32:23.431
[groaning]

32:25.205 --> 32:26.797
Scusi. Scusi.

32:26.907 --> 32:28.568
