32:47.995 --> 32:51.123
[muttering in ltalian accent]

32:52.099 --> 32:54.226
[ And l should have
painted my nails [[

32:54.301 --> 32:56.235
Around, around she goes.

32:56.303 --> 32:58.533
Where she stops,
nobody knows...

32:59.006 --> 33:00.837
but me.

33:02.809 --> 33:04.037
That's it.

33:07.347 --> 33:11.340
Yes, yes, this gonna be
a Section 5.

33:11.585 --> 33:12.643
Easy.

33:16.990 --> 33:18.116
Let's see.

33:25.499 --> 33:28.195
Figoratti, you okay, pal?

33:28.268 --> 33:29.599
Figoratti!

33:37.945 --> 33:39.173
[laughing]

33:39.646 --> 33:41.614
(woman)
Oh, Giancarlo.

33:44.384 --> 33:46.477
John, l wanna
talk to you.

33:46.620 --> 33:47.644
