33:47.721 --> 33:49.621
l feel terrible
about things.

33:49.690 --> 33:50.679
Oh, don't worry.

33:50.757 --> 33:52.725
Lots of things were said
that nobody meant.

33:52.793 --> 33:55.762
No, l don't mean that.
l called the military.

33:58.265 --> 34:00.733
l wish there was something
l could do to rectify it.

34:01.868 --> 34:04.735
